  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/8823264afd2574e24df440469faf1415.poster.avif?t=1767112544\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/8823264afd2574e24df440469faf1415.webm?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/8823264afd2574e24df440469faf1415.mp4?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A minimalistic puzzle where you have to think before you act, one wrong move and 'Pop' chicken could get lost! She knows that there are no dangers on the farm, but things always change places, leaving her confused.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/84872bfbbefc8af30e558085ec61a006.poster.avif?t=1767112544\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/84872bfbbefc8af30e558085ec61a006.webm?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/84872bfbbefc8af30e558085ec61a006.mp4?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Your objective is to save your lost chicks, bringing them to the comfort of the barn, where there is a cozy chicken coop for everyone and abundant affection from a caring mother.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/9d3e68900253fded9bb1a4ee6043d766.poster.avif?t=1767112544\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/9d3e68900253fded9bb1a4ee6043d766.webm?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/9d3e68900253fded9bb1a4ee6043d766.mp4?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 40 handcrafted levels.<br></li><li> Simple and intuitive gameplay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/81326b26c60e193e01dec584eebaa929.poster.avif?t=1767112544\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/81326b26c60e193e01dec584eebaa929.webm?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/81326b26c60e193e01dec584eebaa929.mp4?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> Tips, showing where the barrel will fall and where its offspring are.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/4f2a2aafb0ee6e7bc8ba116a3701f557.poster.avif?t=1767112544\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/4f2a2aafb0ee6e7bc8ba116a3701f557.webm?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/4f2a2aafb0ee6e7bc8ba116a3701f557.mp4?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> Redo function. In case Pop gets lost.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/2beecb7dc0a60669b410948087e8bbe0.poster.avif?t=1767112544\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/2beecb7dc0a60669b410948087e8bbe0.webm?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2453770/extras/2beecb7dc0a60669b410948087e8bbe0.mp4?t=1767112544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> Immersive and cozy soundtrack.<br></li><li> Control a cute chicken. 🐔🐤</li></ul>",
